data.description: Welcome home to this move in ready 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath gem in the sought after Selva Lakes community! Newly installed luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, renovated bathrooms, plantation shutters, and an extended paver patio make this home stand out above the rest. Enjoy year round sunshine in the large, air conditioned sunroom that adds another 225 square feet of living space not reflected on the tax record. The open living room features soaring high ceilings, creating a bright and spacious atmosphere. The kitchen includes a cozy dining nook, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or a quick bite. Its seamless connection to the adjacent dining room creates a fantastic flow, making it an entertainer's dream. Primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings and leads to a stunning bathroom with granite countertops, dual sinks, and a walk in shower with river rock accents. And there's more!...two car garage, community pool, close to the beach and Jack Russel park, and low HOA fees. Don't miss your chance to live the Atlantic Beach lifestyle!.
